name: World united brothers: Danish hotdog and Chinese Juanbing
description: World united brothers: Danish hotdog and Chinese Juanbing :tasty Chinese burrito or pancake. actually it’s a typical Shandong province(a Chinese Northern province ) daily cuisine consisting of flour with meat and green onion wrapped into a slim shape. I am living in Danmark. when a danish mentioned their street food hotdog, it’s visible to see their proud of the unique hotdog which dressed with sour cucumber and fried crispy onion. As a Chinese was born in Shandong province, let me to choose a cuisine as same functional and importance as Danish hotdog, it obviously is Juanbing.By Artist Teng Teng( https://www.instagram.com/tengtengart/).Representative by Bubble Cat Gallery:https://linktr.ee/bubblecatgallery
